title.value: CARIN RTPBC Event Type Value Set

description.value: This value set contains event types used in RTPBC message headers.

title.value: CARIN RTPBC Pharmacy Type Value Setf

description.value: This value set contains a subset of two-letter ISO 3166-1-2 country codes for the countries in which this profile is intended to be used (US and CA).

tr.td: Covered with restriction: Prior authorization required
Covered with restriction: Step therapy applies
Covered with restriction: Quantity limits apply
Covered with restriction: Other restriction applies

title.value: CARIN RTPBC Coverage Summary Value Set

description.value: This value set contains a set of coverage outcomes that may apply to a prescription product and pharmacy combination evaluated in the Real-time Pharmacy Benefit Check (RTPBC) process.

tr.td: Amount to be collected from a patient to be applied to a periodic deductible.
Amount to be collected from a patient to satisfy a per prescription coinsurance.
Amount to be collected from the patient to satisfy a per prescription copay.
Amount to be collected from the patient for sales tax.
Full product cash price before discounts or coupons
Coupon discount reducing the amount to be collected from the patient
Member discount reducing the amount to be collected from the patient
Other discount reducing the amount to be collected from the patient
Other amount to be collected from the patient
Amount equalling the total patient responsibility for a prescription product's cost.

title.value: CARIN RTPBC Patient Pay Type Value Set

description.value: This value set contains components of a patient's responsibility for a prescription product's cost.

title.value: CARIN RTPBC Two Letter State and Province Code Value Set

description.value: This value set contains two letter USPS state codes and Canada Post province codes.
